data.description: This large home features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. With 1,754 square feet of home and an attached garage you'll surely love the space. The custom deck at the back of the house features two built in swings and benches and a large backyard to view. The main level has a remodeled dining space just off of the kitchen along with other noteworthy remodeled spaces within.
